# Stack

- React 19 functional components + hooks only; Vite SPA
- Tailwind v4 + shadcn/ui; single `index.css` token layer
- Hono on Cloudflare Workers for API
- Shared types/Zod in `packages/shared`
- Scripts: `<domain>:<action>` (e.g. `db:migrate`); bare names for aggregates (`dev`, `build`, `check`)
- Kanban drag: optimistic update, reconcile, roll back on failure
